welcome_message_body: Welcome to Wesley Chapel, where Southern charm meets modern amenities. Known for its beautiful landscapes, friendly locals, and vibrant community, we invite you to explore and enjoy all that our city has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Mac Dill AFB Airport serves both civilian and military flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tampa International Airport houses all ticketing, baggage claim, and passenger services.

terminals.name: Airside A
terminals.description: Airside A is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Airside C
terminals.description: Airside C is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, primarily serving Southwest Airlines.

terminals.name: Airside E
terminals.description: Airside E is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, primarily serving Delta and United Airlines.

terminals.name: Airside F
terminals.description: Airside F is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, primarily serving Frontier, JetBlue, and Spirit Airlines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. Premium WiFi is also available for purchase.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Municipal Airport handles all freight and cargo shipments.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free WiFi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Airside Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is for passengers who have cleared security.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Executive Airport serves commercial flights and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Executive Airport caters to private and chartered flights, providing a luxurious and exclusive experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy complimentary WiFi throughout the airport.
